Habits that improve life
===================================

• Exercise
  Walking, running, swimming, yoga, weightlifting, and sports
  Benefits: better sleep, weight management, more energy,
  reduced stress, improved heart health, improved brain health

• Reading
  Reading daily builds knowledge and transforms the mind
  Benefits: improve vocabulary, learn new skills,
  improve current skills, expand knowledge, improve storytelling

• Writing
  Writing daily improves an essential skill
  Necessary for: communication, business, marketing,
  persuasion, expanding thoughts, documenting experiences

• Gratitude
  Being grateful daily improves outlook and emotional state
  Helps see positives, feel lighter, less frustrated

• Meditation
  15-25 minutes daily
  Benefits: increased awareness, focus & memory,
  intuition, emotional regulation, higher stress tolerance

• Plan your day(s)
  Making a to-do list, creating a schedule,
  prioritizing tasks, setting structure,
  realistic deadlines, room for unexpected events

• Waking up early
  “Early bird gets the worm”
  Gives a head start and extra hours to accomplish more

• Art/creativity
  Express yourself through dancing, sports, painting,
  writing, cooking, coding/web design, communication, movies
